</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Baker &amp; Mckenzie, the world's largest law firm, has emerged as the leading
legal adviser on international infrastructure projects in 1993-94, according
to the magazine Privatisation International. Firms are ranked by the number
and value of the transactions they were involved in.
